column2: select a.artistid, a.name as artist, count(t.trackid) as numtracks, count(g.genreid) as numClassical   from chinook.artist a      inner join chinook.album b         on b.artistid=a.artistid      inner join chinook.track t         on t.albumid=b.albumid      left outer join chinook.Genre g         on g.genreid=t.genreid        and g.name=&&&   group by a.artistid,a.name   order by a.name
